HOW TO INSTALL?
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
1. npm install (terminal)                           |
2. npm run build-and-watch-css (terminal)           |
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

What is Tailwind CSS?
1.  CSS framework made up of utility classes
2.  Much lower-level than Bootstrap, Materialize.
-----------------------------------------------------

You Should Know...
1.  Both HTML & CSS
-----------------------------------------------------

Using Tailwind CSS
1.  Install Tailwind using npm (node package manager) - installed in package
2.  You'll need node.js installed on your computer -
-----------------------------------------------------